<item>
            <title>[LU-19482] FLR-EC: Implement FLR state transition logic for EC files</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19482</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Extend the existing File Level Replication (FLR) state machine to support erasure-coded layouts. EC files will follow the same state transition model as mirrored files, including transitions through &lt;tt&gt;RDONLY&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;WRITE_PENDING&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;SYNC_PENDING&lt;/tt&gt;, and related intent handling.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This work is limited to enabling state transition and management logic for EC components. It does &lt;b&gt;not&lt;/b&gt; include I/O support or any operations involving parity components.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
